GEO PRODUCTION ROBOTSpray Robot Technical DescriptionThe spray robot consists of a mechanical steel weldment with servo motor driven 4 wheel drive for floor propulsion and a servo motor driven rack system for spray head cross-traverse.   The system is controlled by a Delta Tau servo control/amplifier system with a PC based user interface system.  The user interface PC utilizes a touch screen for data input.  The system software has a manual and automatic mode.  In manual mode the robot can be controlled via 3 joysticks (1 for the near drive wheels 1 for the far drive wheels and 1 for the cross-traverse of the spray carrier.  In automatic mode the system the user can select pre-programmed recipes.  The recipes can be programmed by selecting step distances step number and speeds.
